研究获新进展</a><p>5、兰科传粉与昆虫协同进化</p><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.kib.ac.cn/xwzx/kyjz/201404/t20140402_4085245.html" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b5cb7f6ef485d7e78ec84be11ced97e8_ipico.jpg" data-image-width="662" data-image-height="800" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">兰科植物产卵地拟态研究取得最新进展----中国科学院昆明植物研究所</a><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.kib.cas.cn/xwzx/cmsm/201104/t20110425_3121056.html" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">狡黠的花朵 受骗的虫--昆明植物所揭示兰科植物传粉生态学机制----中国科学院昆明植物研究所</a><p>6、姜科传粉与昆虫协同进化</p><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.xtbg.ac.cn/xwzx/kydt/201604/t20160427_4591898.html" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-94ee6197c3f0b15f846af94c50e8cb0d_180x120.jpg" data-image-width="749" data-image-height="100" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">走出非洲：喜马拉雅地区植物花部性状与传粉昆虫的协同进化----中国科学院西双版纳热带植物园</a><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.xtbg.ac.cn/xwzx/kydt/201101/t20110110_3055969.html" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-94ee6197c3f0b15f846af94c50e8cb0d_180x120.jpg" data-image-width="749" data-image-height="100" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">象牙参属植物的传粉生态学研究取得新进展----中国科学院西双版纳热带植物园</a><p>7、大戟科传粉与昆虫协同进化</p><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2017/2/368802.shtm" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e5ea52c6f52ec0e0b5d5c2bc74e97d5a_ipico.jpg" data-image-width="200" data-image-height="194" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">算盘子与头细蛾：植物与昆虫的“天作之合”-新闻-科学网</a><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.scib.cas.cn/kycg/kyjz_1/201105/t20110504_3127108.html" data-draft-node="block" data