1.zhimg.com/v2-c3df309f1fe82a9fb9d0b361095a0654_ipico.jpg" data-image-width="165" data-image-height="200" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">华南植物园研究发现新的鸟类传粉植物----中科院华南植物园</a><p>12、水媒/雨媒传粉与昆虫协同进化</p><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.kepu.net.cn/gb/moving/201603/t20160311_20169.html" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-571ee59565c33f43a4e26ce1f433bf9f_180x120.jpg" data-image-width="400" data-image-height="100" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">以水为媒--苦草的漂浮受粉奇遇记-科普动态-中国科普博览</a><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//ecrg.groups.xtbg.ac.cn/%25e7%25a0%2594%25e7%25a9%25b6%25e5%258a%25a8%25e6%2580%2581-2/%25e9%259b%25a8%25e5%25aa%2592%25e4%25bc%25a0%25e7%25b2%2589%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%259c%25ba%25e5%2588%25b6" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">雨媒传粉新机制 | 濒危植物迁地保护与再引种研究组</a><p>传粉生物学博大精深，这里例举若干，权当做抛砖引玉。</p></script><a class="time" href="/question/268412341/answer/345759451">2018-03-19</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>11</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="21798295"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">3 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</butto