ow="q:fi:button" data-id="4974828"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">添加评论</span></button></li><li class="bull">&bull;</li><li><a href="/question/31938573">11 个回答</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-89899751"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/46931232/answer/329080590"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="10986420"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="46931232"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="89899751"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="329080590"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/46931232/answer/329080590">哪一种花香味甜腻，闻起来像甜点一样？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>75</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">75</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/xian-cheng-han" data-hovercard='p$t$xian-cheng-han'>跌水繁落</a>，<span title="养花者，喜欢冷门花卉，欢迎同好互相交流信息。尽自己所能，使每个回答都有收藏价值。" class="bio">养花者，喜欢冷门花卉，欢迎同好互相交流信息。尽自己所能，使每个回答都有收藏价值。</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="跌水繁落" data-entry-url="/question/46931232/answer/329080590"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">按题目要求就是感觉能吃的香味吧1.巧克力香味（1）巧克力秋英巧克力加香草的味道。（2）<i>Hibiscus waimeae</i>据说是木槿香调为中调，后期会呈现巧克力，肉豆蔻香调的味道。(3)金露花据说是牛奶加巧克力的味道喔。另外一提，同属的黄素梅是难闻的橡皮泥味儿。 2.…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/46931232/answer/329080590">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="75"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/diao-diao-diao-diao-diao-24" data-hovercard='p$t$diao-diao-diao-diao-diao-24'>曾有一藏剑</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/sheng-gao-yan-58" data-hovercard='p$t$sheng-gao-yan-58'>幸福终点站</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/lily-83-15" data-hovercard='p$t$lily-83-15'>Lily</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>按题目要求就是感觉能吃的香味吧</p><p>1.巧克力香味</p><p>（1）巧克力秋英</p><p>巧克力加香草的味道。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b8a638e71acd0650fe9906212d40fb02_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="400" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b8a638e71acd0650fe9906212d40fb02_r.jpg"></figure><p>（2）<i>Hibiscus waimeae</i></p><p>据说是木槿香调为中调，后期会呈现巧克力，肉豆蔻香调的味道。</p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c5bd5bbdeb437826d7896442005fc559_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="1067" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c5bd5bbdeb437826d7896442005fc559_r.jpg"></figure><p>(3)金露花</p><p>据说是牛奶加巧克力的味道喔。</p><p>另外一提，同属的黄素梅是难闻的橡皮泥味儿。<br><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-01113c6b317833f18ed708c423f1d224_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="601" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="601" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-01113c6b317833f18ed708c423f1d224_r.jpg"></figure><br></p><p>2.柑橘香</p><p>月季真宙应该是比较典型的柑橘香了，不过有人觉得是烂红薯味。。。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b96e90c2d08dfaa030e5e70e97447d33_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="500" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b96e90c2d08dfaa030e5e70e97447d33_r.jpg"></figure><p>3.大马士革玫瑰香</p><p>可能有人不是特别清楚，虽然月季蜻蜓看上去很忧郁，但香调却是浓郁的大马士革玫瑰香附带辛辣香调，和它外表完全不符合的香调啊。。。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-03d8f1e29fc83a5e124a9aed10ce679e_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="493" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="493" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-03d8f1e29fc83a5e124a9aed10ce679e_r.jpg"></figure><p>4.茴香香</p><p>名如其实，茴香酒夫人月季是强烈的茴香味儿，这个味道类似榴莲味儿，并不是那么讨喜。另外纽曼姐妹也是典型的茴香香</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa1ef64f5c15d5de30d4475d8870db05_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="532" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa1ef64f5c15d5de30d4475d8870db05_r.jpg"></figure><p>5.桃子香</p><p>桃香，名如其实。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b495d5658fe85e7227df9f4f8988378_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b495d5658fe85e7227df9f4f8988378_r.jpg"></figure><p>6.荔枝香</p><p>银禧庆典的香味可以闻出草莓、柑橘、荔枝的味道。（因人而异）</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a99d85747476b98a03dbadd9f0d410e_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a99d85747476b98a03dbadd9f0d410e_r.jpg"></figure><p>好了，月季的水果香型到此打住，反正月季许多品种都能开得出，至于你会闻出什么，梨子、葡萄、醋栗、覆盆子之类的，因你体质而异。但热带水果的香味，基本没有。</p><p>7.肉桂味</p><p>纪念马赛尔普鲁斯特</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-babb7dc14b3e8545c6c357d35eabbc13_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-babb7dc14b3e8545c6c357d35eabbc13_r.jpg"></figure>8.熟苹果香<br>睡莲艳阳是少数香味明确描述有特定水果味道的睡莲品种，但综合素质不是特别优秀，说起来柑橘香在睡莲里也挺常见的。<br><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-812c1383d624263136064e1896fc038e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="500" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-812c1383d624263136064e1896fc038e_r.jpg"></figure>9.香蕉香<br>含笑是种神奇的植物，有浓郁的香蕉味儿,而且因人而异，有人则是闻到了青苹果的味道呢。<br><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fba0193fbb76c24da671356529881d10_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="402" data-rawheight="301" class="content_image" width="402"></figure>10.奶油香<br>文心兰部分品种是奶油香气或者说是奶香，也有巧克力味儿的。<br><br><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-01fc98aab161f46e0cb930d11eeb2a9d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="576" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="576" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-01fc98aab161f46e0cb930d11eeb2a9d_r.jpg"></figure></script><a class="time" href="/question/46931232/answer/329080590">2018-02-26</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>75</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="10986420"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">38 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zh