20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/rosecrimson" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$rosecrimson'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9a9528c47fe72f12db921b2f408bc601_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="蔓玫"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/flower2018/rosecrimson/answers" class="answers text-muted">15 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/rosecrimson" data-hovercard='p$t$rosecrimson'>蔓玫</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">尔曹身与名俱灭，不废江河万古流。</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/xiaocheng-smalltown" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$xiaocheng-smalltown'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9aeab937a885afb98c24bf763bcc50ef_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="小铖"></img></a><div class="content"><a class="name author-link" href="/people/xiaocheng-smalltown" data-hovercard='p$t$xiaocheng-smalltown'>小铖</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">《花卉》杂志社 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 杂志编辑</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/linshizhi" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$linshizhi'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-53600c69f129e458dbc9fb1a2d6c2a44_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="林十之"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/flower2018/linshizhi/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/linshizhi" data-hovercard='p$t$linshizhi'>林十之</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" 